Because if the African people.
and the African governments

01:15:09.200 --> 01:15:10.854
don't want to
preserve the wildlife.

01:15:10.941 --> 01:15:12.769
there's really nothing that
we can do from the outside.

01:15:12.856 --> 01:15:15.554
Our job actually is to
convince them that it's

01:15:15.641 --> 01:15:18.688
in their best interest
to preserve these animals

01:15:18.775 --> 01:15:19.602
for the future.

01:15:22.387 --> 01:15:25.129
- We cannot tell
local communities.

