"is no longer a nuisance
to you. it's going

01:15:42.712 --> 01:15:44.627
"to bring these
amount of people.

01:15:44.714 --> 01:15:47.630
"Even if it kills a cow
now and again. so what?

01:15:47.717 --> 01:15:49.153
"This is what it brings in."

01:15:50.415 --> 01:15:53.070
But it has to go to the people.

01:15:53.157 --> 01:15:55.812
the people have
to get the money.

