- [Narrator] The
Baka people have

01:16:48.299 --> 01:16:50.475
over 15 words for elephant.

01:16:51.781 --> 01:16:54.566
- If the argument is
that. we need the wealth

01:16:54.653 --> 01:16:57.264
under the land. the
diamonds. minerals.

01:16:57.351 --> 01:16:59.005
petroleum. and so forth.

01:16:59.092 --> 01:17:00.833
If you look at the countries.

01:17:00.920 --> 01:17:04.402
which have the most valuable
of these resources in Africa.

01:17:04.489 --> 01:17:06.447
say. where they've
been exploited already

01:17:06.534 --> 01:17:08.319
for a hundred years or more.

01:17:08.406 --> 01:17:11.235
These are still amongst the
poorest countries in the world.

01:17:11.322 --> 01:17:14.020
So. it hasn't benefited
the local people.

01:17:16.370 --> 01:17:18.895
It is colonialism to remove
people from their land.

01:17:18.982 --> 01:17:22.855
and it's also racist.
and it's also illegal.

01:17:24.335 --> 01:17:27.294
And it's time to respect
the people who have lived

01:17:27.381 --> 01:17:30.515
in these places for.
for essentially forever

01:17:30.602 --> 01:17:32.996
and to accept the fact
that they have rights.

01:17:33.083 --> 01:17:36.216
just like we claim
for ourselves.

01:17:38.175 --> 01:17:40.177
In Cameroon there's
still parks being created

01:17:40.264 --> 01:17:41.918
and other protected zones.

01:17:42.005 --> 01:17:43.746
Some of them are
for trophy hunting.

01:17:43.833 --> 01:17:45.530
So if you pay a lot
of money you can go

01:17:45.617 --> 01:17:49.099
and hunt a forest
elephant. for example.

01:17:49.186 --> 01:17:51.971
Although that's actually
an endangered species.

01:17:52.058 --> 01:17:55.366
There are areas. which
are adjacent to the parks.

01:17:55.453 --> 01:17:58.282
which are so-called protected.
some are for logging.

01:17:58.369 --> 01:18:00.414
some are for trophy hunting.

01:18:01.589 --> 01:18:05.768
The Baka are evicted
and pushed to the edge

01:18:05.855 --> 01:18:07.204
and outside the park.

01:18:07.291 --> 01:18:10.033
where their society
is entirely smashed.

01:18:10.120 --> 01:18:14.211
They turn to drink.
there are no jobs.

01:18:14.298 --> 01:18:18.084
It's not as if we're offering
these people an alternative.

01:18:18.171 --> 01:18:19.433
Tribal peoples have lived

01:18:19.520 --> 01:18:21.305
on these lands
essentially forever.

01:18:22.741 --> 01:18:26.049
The Baka. so-called pygmies.
they are stewards of the land.

01:18:26.136 --> 01:18:29.661
They know how to look
after it and how to look

01:18:29.748 --> 01:18:31.228
after the animals.
which they use.

01:18:31.315 --> 01:18:32.751
including the ones they hunt.

01:18:34.579 --> 01:18:38.496
[speaking in Baka language]

01:19:00.866 --> 01:19:03.434
We're stealing their land
in order to set up parks

01:19:05.958 --> 01:19:08.482
and to satisfy conservationists
and for tourism.

01:19:10.180 --> 01:19:12.051
Lodges are built.
roads are built.

01:19:13.487 --> 01:19:15.228
There is often harassment
of the animals.

01:19:19.015 --> 01:19:19.842
And that is actually
extremely dangerous

01:19:21.539 --> 01:19:22.758
because it makes them more
likely to attack people

01:19:22.845 --> 01:19:22.932
if people are
outside the vehicles.

01:19:28.024 --> 01:19:30.243
Whereas formerly they
would have just run away

01:19:30.330 --> 01:19:32.028
and avoided people all together.

01:19:32.115 --> 01:19:34.726
so it changes animal behavior.

01:19:37.729 --> 01:19:42.734
There's several layers of this
con trick in conservation.

01:19:44.127 --> 01:19:46.346
One is that these lands are
empty of peoples when in fact.

01:19:46.433 --> 01:19:48.827
they've been emptied
of peoples. forcibly.

01:19:48.914 --> 01:19:51.264
often to make the
conservation zones.

01:19:52.439 --> 01:19:56.313
[speaking in Baka language]

01:21:02.074 --> 01:21:05.295
Another is that the outside
conservationists are somehow

01:21:05.382 --> 01:21:08.951
or other better at
preserving the environment.

01:21:09.038 --> 01:21:11.257
preserving the eco-diversity.

01:21:11.344 --> 01:21:13.129
than the people who live there.

01:21:13.216 --> 01:21:16.784
And actually there's almost
no scientific evidence

01:21:16.872 --> 01:21:19.048
to support that and
the scientific evidence

01:21:19.135 --> 01:21:21.964
is in actually completely
the other direction.

