01:21:29.058 --> 01:21:31.756
- What we need to do is
make sure that businesses

01:21:31.843 --> 01:21:34.324
are doing what people
want and what people want

01:21:34.411 --> 01:21:38.458
is to have a world. which is
looking after their interests.

01:21:38.545 --> 01:21:39.851
is looking after
nature's interests.

01:21:39.938 --> 01:21:41.679
is looking after
society's interests.

01:21:42.854 --> 01:21:44.508
One of the solutions
that we can bring

01:21:44.595 --> 01:21:48.077
into this complex problem
is around natural capital.

01:21:49.556 --> 01:21:52.342
And this model that we used
to have. of cutting it off.

01:21:52.429 --> 01:21:54.910
fencing it off. making
sure that it was protected.

01:21:54.997 --> 01:21:58.348
Conserving. that
word conservation is
about protecting it.

01:21:58.435 --> 01:21:59.610
and making sure
no one goes there.

01:21:59.697 --> 01:22:01.177
That isn't conservation.

01:22:01.264 --> 01:22:03.266
Conservation is making
sure we're understanding

01:22:03.353 --> 01:22:06.922
how dependent we are on it.
the benefits it gives us.

01:22:08.793 --> 01:22:13.537
So. the idea that we should
have control over it.

01:22:13.624 --> 01:22:16.540
we should fence it off.
means that we have to keep on

01:22:16.627 --> 01:22:18.237
paying to protect it.

01:22:18.324 --> 01:22:20.022
So. we work with the
local people. we work

01:22:20.109 --> 01:22:22.763
with the local animals.
the local species.

01:22:22.850 --> 01:22:24.374
If we can work with them.

01:22:24.461 --> 01:22:27.116
then it ends up becoming
self-sustaining.

01:22:27.203 --> 01:22:30.554
Otherwise we end up having to
pay all the time to protect.

01:22:30.641 --> 01:22:31.990
We have to pay for rangers.

01:22:32.077 --> 01:22:33.818
we have to pay for
protections systems.

01:22:33.905 --> 01:22:36.952
But we can only do that if
we can understand the value

01:22:37.039 --> 01:22:38.692
that it's delivering to us.

01:22:38.779 --> 01:22:41.739
Otherwise what is the
cost of doing that?

01:22:41.826 --> 01:22:44.524
How do we fit that
in our conversation?

01:22:45.656 --> 01:22:48.528
[chimp screeching]

